# Database Connection Secrets (Template)
#
# This is a TEMPLATE file showing the structure of database secrets.
# DO NOT put real values here. DO NOT commit this with real values.
#
# To create encrypted version:
# 1. Copy this file: cp database.env.example /tmp/database-dev.env
# 2. Fill in real values in /tmp/database-dev.env
# 3. Encrypt: sops --encrypt /tmp/database-dev.env > database-dev.env.enc
# 4. Delete plaintext: rm /tmp/database-dev.env
